y1=a^265*x[2]+a^264*x[3]+a^263*x[4]+...+a^0*x[267]

y2=a^264*x[4]+a^263*x[5]+a^263*x[6]+...+a^0*x[268]

....

y265=a^1*x[530]+a^0*x[531]

y266=a^0*x[532]

Could anyone give me some advice how can I achieve this?
